Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:07.60,bwT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I had always thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:12.30,bwT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,that one day I would become someone special.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:13.80,bwT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,One day,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:17.51,bwT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I would find something where it was clear I had talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:20.92,bwT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,For a long time now,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:26.17,bwT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I had always imagined that I was a knight who had fought many battles to protect a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:27.77,bwT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:31.75,bwT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,it seems I didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:33.50,bwT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:43.52,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I liked that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:49.10,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,The quiet, empty train station where nobody came was the best place for reading alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:53.15,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:55.45,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,someone got here before me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:05.89,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,N-No trains come to this station.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:11.98,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:14.11,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.95,0:01:16.83,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.92,0:01:21.78,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Today was the first time I met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:24.06,MainT,Renji&Sign,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:26.71,MainT,Renji&Sign,0000,0000,0000,,an encounter that lasted less than forty-five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:15.48,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Argh, I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:19.94,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should go and do some research.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.95,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's just Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:26.27,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:28.77,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, don't forget about the party!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:31.18,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:33.24,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll stop by there on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:54.52,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:03:57.77,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get a good shot, Kyosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:04:00.15,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I only take good shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:03.45,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,If it snowed, that would be the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.73,0:04:04.64,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.71,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,That would make it difficult when you edit later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:07.80,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:09.79,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,The library has it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:11.39,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:12.08,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:29.86,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:33.85,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I was thinking it would be nice to take a shot for the cushion too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:37.98,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,There must've been a pretty girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:41.52,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Again? Is that it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:43.99,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, that hurts. O-O-O-Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:46.55,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:49.03,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, welcome back, Kei-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:50.98,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:53.16,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,The bakery was crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:55.37,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, where's onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:57.37,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,He's not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:01.43,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious? I wonder if he's really coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:04.38,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I told him I wouldn't let him off if he stood us up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:07.76,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-senpai always seems to be busy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:09.72,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,even though he's not in a club or cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:11.63,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he has his reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:13.72,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki, help me set them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:14.62,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:17.40,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,But he's a weird person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:20.19,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, when it looked like he was deep in thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:22.65,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,he suddenly started scratching his head like crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:25.60,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,As if he were a manga artist facing a deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:30.20,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kei-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:32.30,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:34.12,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send him another e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:41.29,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas, onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:43.04,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:56.64,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:03.48,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, so this is how it looks inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.61,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:12.37,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Mass has already ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:15.59,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, nah, I'm not a believer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:17.50,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just here to do some research.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:18.69,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:22.71,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone I have to meet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:24.71,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're waiting for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:30.72,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be leaving then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:32.72,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:34.14,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:36.27,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:39.98,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:43.74,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:46.40,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You're late. Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:49.81,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ack, Kei is mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:51.91,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:54.28,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:57.75,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you see a bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:06:58.86,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:07:00.33,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know which way it went?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:01.17,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,That way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:04.20,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I'm borrowing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:11.32,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:12.92,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,My... bicycle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:14.43,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You bicycle thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:16.52,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:18.15,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,It's not "hello."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:22.06,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, don't tell me you forgot about the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:23.29,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:24.69,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just standing you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:27.54,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that defiant attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:30.85,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a dress for the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:32.67,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Snow White?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:34.95,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, right now I'm Cinderella.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:36.67,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,They're the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:38.41,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time for that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:42.42,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Could it be that you got an urgent job?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:45.14,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm busy right now. We'll talk next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:47.38,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,"We'll talk next time," you say... eh, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:54.90,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, you idiot! Go die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:57.60,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:04.52,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,My bicycle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:08.27,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:14.53,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Is this 119?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:21.27,MainT,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,When the ambulance gets here, I have to go with her, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:24.01,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:35.24,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,She's alive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:37.76,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,She can't be dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:42.19,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:46.76,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,What was I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.76,0:08:49.19,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:50.82,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:53.32,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.13,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You have to lie there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:56.71,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I was robbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:59.38,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,My important bag was stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:01.26,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do if you hit your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:03.44,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Wait till the ambulance gets here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:06.30,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,No, that bag was expensive,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:08.86,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,and both my wallet and cell phone were inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.96,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:12.95,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:21.72,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Being in the park at night calms you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:24.24,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What about the purse-snatcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:27.13,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you'd definitely catch him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:29.08,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I ran too much and got tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:31.00,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You give up quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.61,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:35.46,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,There's no money in my wallet anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:38.77,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,and the only number on my cell phone is my grandma's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:41.62,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I was thinking of buying a new bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:45.97,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.97,0:09:48.62,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's totally different from what you said earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:52.47,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:54.80,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt somewhere, or do you feel like throwing up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:58.76,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:01.63,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you just don't feel the symptoms yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:03.05,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You did pass out after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:05.38,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't pass out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:07.54,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You lost consciousness just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:10.43,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,No way, I don't remember it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:13.74,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you'd remember passing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:14.78,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:22.11,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:25.29,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.79,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:31.54,bw,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:33.36,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You're nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:34.57,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:37.53,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's better for you if you went to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.30,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:41.58,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:45.07,bw,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It's snow. Snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.76,0:10:48.57,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:51.06,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:57.60,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:11:01.35,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,To have a white Christmas like this with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:02.99,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:05.00,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, how cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:08.14,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it sad to be alone on a day like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:09.74,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:12.04,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I can live just by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:15.71,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:21.09,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't told you my name, have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:23.13,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Miyamura Miyako.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:25.63,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hirono Hiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:28.44,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono Hiro... Hiro Hiro, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:30.26,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,What a strange name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.26,0:11:33.59,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you the same? Miyamura Miyako, Miya Miya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:35.56,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:38.78,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You found something interesting. You're smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:41.95,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Hirono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:43.66,bw,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:45.45,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:47.45,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,at my home tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:53.19,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You were thinking of something perverted, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:53.99,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:55.58,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:12:01.34,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, my house key was in that bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:02.84,bw,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:06.90,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get into my house even if I go back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:10.26,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I have to stay out tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:11.21,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,On that subject,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:15.65,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,isn't it dangerous for a girl to stay out by herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:19.02,bw,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... you want me to come along with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:22.28,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there a saying, "One might as well be hanged for a sheep as a lamb"?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.00,0:12:22.28,Notes Box,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\be1\org(0,10000)\frx-0.015\t(0,613,0.25,\frx0)}A
Dialogue: 2,0:12:19.00,0:12:22.28,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,10000)\frx-0.015\t(0,613,0.25,\frx0)}The original idiom is "doku wo kurawaba sara made." 【毒を食らわば皿まで】
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:24.01,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Come, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:26.31,Main2,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, w-wait. I'm not coming with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.31,0:12:28.21,Main2,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've still got things to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:27.02,MainT,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that Christmas this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:31.40,MainT,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,isn't ending just yet.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.79,0:12:39.80,Notes Box,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\be1}A
Dialogue: 2,0:12:36.79,0:12:39.80,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Risou," which means "Dream."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:47.16,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,During homeroom after school,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:49.95,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,the printouts from the career interest survey were handed out to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:53.73,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike the dream of the future we had when we were children,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:56.71,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,we now have to define our future concretely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:13:01.79,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,"I want to be a prince who fights to protect a princess from disasters."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:06.32,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm far past the age that would allow me to write down a dream like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:10.90,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:12.49,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:16.21,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,And... why are you asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.50,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear an adult's opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:22.84,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Himura-san might be able to give me some good advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:27.09,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to disappoint you, but I'm not a pastor, or a counselor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:29.88,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,But since you're always here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:32.72,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,it's natural for me to approach you for advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:35.91,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just waiting for someone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.16,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You're waiting for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:40.73,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:43.20,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What do I like...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:44.88,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Reading, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:46.61,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I like fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:48.62,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You can go with that then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:52.00,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,After you graduate from a liberal arts college, you can work in something related to publishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:53.79,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You can also write fiction yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:58.54,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,But, isn't it too hasty to just turn something I like into my job?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:14:01.93,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's a thousand times better than doing something you hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:04.25,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:07.80,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,No more advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:10.80,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,This is my "adult's opinion."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:13.56,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Adult's... opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:16.38,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I understand it, but I don't really get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:20.04,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I have to think it through myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:25.15,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,He made it sound so simple...
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.94,0:14:28.70,Notes Box,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs36}A
Dialogue: 2,0:14:25.94,0:14:28.70,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Omoi," which means "Feeling."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:38.38,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:40.60,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:43.02,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Did I interrupt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:44.02,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:48.89,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, can I ask you something weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:51.85,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Did we meet before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:53.23,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:54.66,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:57.78,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. As I thought, we did meet before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:15:00.68,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Well, actually we just said "hi" to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.68,0:15:02.41,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:08.11,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,E-Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:09.32,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:11.72,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Do you always come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:14.12,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. Just now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:16.62,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,This is a nice, quiet place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:18.08,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:20.22,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's the most suitable place for reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:23.63,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I can openly act out "Stand By Me" here.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.50,0:15:23.61,Notes Box,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,10000)\frx-0.015\t(0,500,0.25,\frx0)}{\fs36\be1}A
Dialogue: 2,0:15:19.50,0:15:23.61,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,10000)\frx-0.015\t(0,500,0.25,\frx0)}Renji is referring to the {\fsp-3}1{\fsp1}986 movie "Stand By Me," directed by Rob Reiner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:26.96,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I mean walking on the railroad track.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:28.80,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,No one will scold me if I do it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:33.66,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.43,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:38.06,Main,Chihiro&Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.42,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:42.77,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Shindou Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:45.72,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Lions drop their cubs into an abysmal valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:48.15,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's written as Senjin and read as Chihiro.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.00,0:15:48.15,Notes Box,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,10000)\frx-0.015\t(0,500,0.25,\frx0)}{\fs36\be1}A
Dialogue: 2,0:15:42.00,0:15:48.15,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,10000)\frx-0.015\t(0,500,0.25,\frx0)}Abysmal valley = 千尋の谷 (senjin no tani). 千尋 is how her name is written.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:50.40,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Asou Renji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:52.24,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Asou-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:53.06,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:55.34,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro, you're early.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:56.46,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Early?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:57.19,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.19,0:16:00.65,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You came earlier than me the other day as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.37,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:05.38,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not attending school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:08.88,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You're not... going to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:10.13,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:12.63,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:13.73,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.88,0:16:17.35,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:21.35,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:23.02,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:25.24,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,This is your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:29.02,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm bothering you, and you seem to feel uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:30.63,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:32.81,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:35.20,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking something similar too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:39.03,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm here, you can't take your time to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:41.37,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:42.66,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:45.42,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Same for me. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:55.68,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll walk you home. Do you live nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:59.55,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I want to stay here a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:01.18,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting dark already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:02.93,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.06,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:06.81,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:11.94,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can I still come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:15.20,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:17.72,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:21.70,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,See you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:22.59,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,...you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:25.21,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:26.54,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.22,0:17:29.42,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,See... you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:31.07,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.68,0:17:40.18,Notes Box,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\be1}A
Dialogue: 2,0:17:37.68,0:17:40.18,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Negai," which means "Wish."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:48.60,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What were you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:51.64,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't looking at anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:52.71,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What about the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:54.61,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:56.74,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:17:59.74,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:02.37,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:05.48,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you look different from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:06.83,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:11.71,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, could you be Asou-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:12.46,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:13.96,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:16.01,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:19.30,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday's "see you"...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:21.63,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday's... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:23.96,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"See you"...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:33.24,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, wh-what's wrong, Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:35.50,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:37.56,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's not. It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:40.31,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no. Why... did I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:42.52,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you ask me why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:44.00,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:46.11,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,This is not what I meant to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:48.85,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:51.13,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:54.05,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:19:01.97,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, why did you come today, Asou-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:04.26,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, well, it's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.76,0:19:06.60,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't really know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.23,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:09.92,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:13.07,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I was too happy and misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.58,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:17.48,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:21.43,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean she was happy to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:23.65,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,But we've only met three times,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:25.54,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,she couldn't be {\i0}so{\i1} happy that she'd hug me and cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:27.60,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.99,0:19:29.37,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Asou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.39,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That pocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:35.51,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's the novel I'm currently reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.51,0:19:38.00,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like fiction?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:41.14,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's like I'm a wordaholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:43.68,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I always carry a few books in my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:47.39,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't, it feels unnatural, as if I'm not carrying enough weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.39,0:19:49.89,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like a cat's whiskers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:52.89,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:54.64,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:58.40,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,That book of yours is like a cat's whiskers too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:00.14,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.14,0:20:02.52,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I can't live without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:04.22,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:05.41,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:11.75,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Asou-san, I have a favor to ask you. May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:13.00,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:15.01,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:17.75,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,be friends with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:19.50,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:22.26,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:24.44,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nah, of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:27.01,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who'd like to ask you to be my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:28.79,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:33.39,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:35.45,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:38.01,Main,Chihiro&Sign,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:43.73,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:47.94,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Asou-san went home after saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:49.36,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:55.12,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Asou-san made a promise to me yesterday, and he came to see me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:20:59.85,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Today he also promised me that he would come see me tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:04.30,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,And he became friends with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:15.75,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I shouldn't indulge myself in something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:19.07,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.49,0:23:39.02,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us meet again, and the uncertain time begins to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.74,0:23:43.44,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(2318,3681,\1c&HE0E0E0&\3c&HE0E0E0&\4c&HE0E0E0&)}Next episode, ef - a tale of memories:
